Show config paths, executable/helper availability, and integration status

Usage: doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --install-missing
          Install missing OpenCode 2, tokei, and ctags with global mise config

      --install-sighthound
          Source-build pinned Sighthound with Rust 1.96 and global mise config

      --check
          Validate the effective oy agent, commands, skills, and models; exit nonzero on failure

  -h, --help
          Print help
